Package net.sf.mmm.util.lang.base.datatype.descriptor Description

Contains the basic implementation of the Util Lang API for datatype description.

Util Lang Base Datatype Descriptor

This package contains the implementations of DatatypeDescriptorManager, DatatypeDescriptor, and DatatypeSegmentDescriptor.
